		<div class="services-description">
			<h2>A Perfect Plan For Your Brand vs Another Sales Pitch</h2>

				<p>
				The fall of most businesses' marketing strategy starts with a pitch from a great sales person.  Most sales people can careless if you need their service or not, they just looking for an quick sale.  330 Monday have a different philsophy.  We excel at creating interactive campaigns thru exhibitions, social media and microsites.  We provide an overall marketing strategy that will fit your business even if we feel you don't need our great interactive campaigns.  We realize that certain marketing channels and initiatives work great for certain goals and may not for others.
				</p>
				<p>
				Instead of settling on a pitch, let us analyze your goals, options and create a plan that will work for your business goals and budget.  Everyday there are new marketing platforms and initiatives to reach your audience.  Its important to know which platforms your audience is using and using those platforms correctly to connect with your audience.  We help sort through the many options and choose the best platforms for your business.</p>
				<p>
				There are many social media platfroms from Facebook, Twitter, Instagram and others.  Are you using the right ones to reach your audience?  People love attending festivals and events, are you engaging with this audience?  Customers are on their phone, tablets and computer all day, is your business making a great impression on the many devices?  Your customers are rating your service or product everyday, how is your reputation?
				</p>
				<p>
				If your business is looking for a forward thinking direction.  Contact 330 Monday to help with your marketing strategies and provide you new and exciting ideas to connect with your audience and accomplish your business goals.
			</p>




		</div>


